Pyramid-Exploration
Navigate the 3D map to get from start to finish using a 2D view of the world

to play the game:
  1.compile the java code in a folder with the maps ("hard1.txt","easy1.txt","beginner1.txt") and the jpg
  2.run the program
  3.input a map name without the ".txt" at the end, for example: hard1
  4.use "a" to go left, "d" to go right, and "s" to switch view
  5.you are trying to get to the dot on the mini map in the bottom right corner
